prompts.frontCover:
A dreamy fantasy anime style birthday card front cover, flat 2D illustration. In the center, a cartoon illustration of a young East Asian couple based on the reference photo (UID: 088bb499-a341-4080-a90e-8ecb230b88f2). The woman, in her early 20s with long, straight black hair parted in the middle and wearing thin-rimmed round glasses, is in front. She's wearing a light blue crewneck sweatshirt with a circular graphic and has a warm, happy smile. The man, also in his early 20s with short, tousled black hair, is hugging her from behind. He wears a tan hoodie and has a big, happy smile. They are comically trying to balance a giant, wobbly, multi-layered birthday cake that is whimsically decorated with sparkling frosting, glowing candy gems, and miniature floating stars. Around them is a magical, enchanted forest scene with oversized, glowing mushrooms, fireflies that leave trails of light, and pastel-colored, whimsical trees with softly swirling leaves. The overall atmosphere is enchanting and lighthearted, with a soft pastel color palette of lavender, mint green, and baby pink. In the center of the scene, floating amidst the magical elements, is the text "Happy Birthday" written in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive script.

- Reference photos provided for character creation
- Characters should only appear on the front cover
- Transform real people into artistic cartoon/illustrated versions matching the style
- Maintain recognizable features while adapting to the artistic style
